                                課程簡介
                            

                                 
                            

                                 
                            

                                Introduction
                            





                                自2010年起, 大智移雲已成為產業重要的科技應用關鍵; 因此, 為呼應此一應用趨勢, 本課程結合資策會大數據所的研發與應用產出, 開設本課程, 希望透過實作與講課方式, 讓同學實際體驗整個巨量資料的應用範疇, 從而作為後續巨量資料應用與技能養成的基礎.

《 課程簡介 -- English 》
                                Since 2010s, applications of big data, smart devices, mobile commerce, and cloud computing have been regarded as keys for developing innovative IT-enabled services for industries. As a result, to react to this trend and business needs, this course aims to introduce fundamentals and basic skills of big data applications for students majoring in MIS. Current practices developed by III are taken as the core of this course.











